  "3088400": {
    "name": "Deadly Trick",
    "steam_appid": 3088400,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088400/extras/b891c62170a114262fd04a005bddfe90.avif?t=1772082104\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088400/extras_big/b891c62170a114262fd04a005bddfe90.avif?t=1772082104 width=800 height=286 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>'Deadly Trick' 是一款二次元风格的社会生存推理游戏！</strong> <br>你的最终目标是完成班级活动, 并在Lastope学校致命의 “特别课程” 中存活下来。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088400/extras/3a641da5f009081c183c9d99ceeeca2d.poster.avif?t=1772082104\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088400/extras/3a641da5f009081c183c9d99ceeeca2d.webm?t=1772082104\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088400/extras/3a641da5f009081c183c9d99ceeeca2d.mp4?t=1772082104\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>召集你的好友，一起加入游戏吧！</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >'Deadly Trick' 支持 5 到 8 人共同游玩。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088400/extras/f9295e52f3317ea7fcd1577ca58bb81e.poster.avif?t=1772082104\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088400/extras/f9295e52f3317ea7fcd1577ca58bb81e.webm?t=1772082104\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088400/extras/f9295e52f3317ea7fcd1577ca58bb81e.mp4?t=1772082104\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>在 'Deadly Trick' 中，玩家可以自主选择身份。</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >根据你的选择，你可以成为善良的 “白方”，或是冷酷的 “黑方”！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088400/extras/131c209e25358d04a7ef9edadad3f1c6.poster.avif?t=1772082104\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088400/extras/131c209e25358d04a7ef9edadad3f1c6.webm?t=1772082104\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088400/extras/131c209e25358d04a7ef9edadad3f1c6.mp4?t=1772082104\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>如果你选择成为白方：</strong> 请完成班级活动，并逃离学校！<strong> </strong> <br>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088400/extras/9f4d9550da931c17fbde7b312a42f375.poster.avif?t=1772082104\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088400/extras/9f4d9550da931c17fbde7b312a42f375.webm?t=1772082104\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088400/extras/9f4d9550da931c17fbde7b312a42f375.mp4?t=1772082104\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>如果你决定成为黑方……</strong> 请秘密除掉其他的参与者！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088400/extras/03c40a2567b881305d465a9c12e9c0cf.poster.avif?t=1772082104\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088400/extras/03c40a2567b881305d465a9c12e9c0cf.webm?t=1772082104\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088400/extras/03c40a2567b881305d465a9c12e9c0cf.mp4?t=1772082104\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>当案件发生时，调查随即开始。</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家需要在案发现场搜集线索，找出谁才是真正的黑方。 在调查结束后的 “学级裁判” 中，你必须指认出凶手。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果在裁判中未能准确指出凶手……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088400/extras/2d6da333c7415a9fa5aad4b68245153c.poster.avif?t=1772082104\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088400/extras/2d6da333c7415a9fa5aad4b68245153c.webm?t=1772082104\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088400/extras/2d6da333c7415a9fa5aad4b68245153c.mp4?t=1772082104\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>除了黑方以外，所有人都会被立即处决。</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这就是为什么彻底的讨论和推导出真正的黑方至关重要的原因！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088400/extras/5af43513c3eb7cdc691bee83bbe781dd.poster.avif?t=1772082104\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088400/extras/5af43513c3eb7cdc691bee83bbe781dd.webm?t=1772082104\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088400/extras/5af43513c3eb7cdc691bee83bbe781dd.mp4?t=1772082104\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088400/extras/3acb7bdad61bb3a8f6a4e0c8b13c98fb.poster.avif?t=1772082104\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088400/extras/3acb7bdad61bb3a8f6a4e0c8b13c98fb.webm?t=1772082104\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088400/extras/3acb7bdad61bb3a8f6a4e0c8b13c98fb.mp4?t=1772082104\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>将搜集到的线索整理成 </strong>“<strong>命题</strong>”<strong>，</strong> 分享并审查彼此的命题， 利用它们推进你的推理，抓捕凶手！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088400/extras/7adc0e26e69c8090377ad7a26c23bd41.poster.avif?t=1772082104\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088400/extras/7adc0e26e69c8090377ad7a26c23bd41.webm?t=1772082104\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088400/extras/7adc0e26e69c8090377ad7a26c23bd41.mp4?t=1772082104\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>一旦你找到了凶手……</strong> 他必须付出应有的代价！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
